column45: that she plans to flee her abusive aunt
column46: he unexpectedly kills her with his snake fangs. Upon opening her eyes
column47: she finds herself in the past
column48: before she met that rotten prince. With her knowledge of the future
column49: she sets off to her father's duchy to strike a deal and change her fate
column50:
but is surprised to find her lion family welcoming her with open arms. Will the stars be on her side so she can rewrite history and get her revenge?

fa:"برتی، سنجاب ضعیفی بود که تو خانواده شیرها به دنیا اومد، پس مجبور شد تو این موقعیت خونه خالش زندگی کنه. شاهزاده دوم ریتر تنها دوست و نامزد اون بود. لحظه ای که گفت برای رسیدن به آرزوش میره… "ریتر، حرومزاده...!" اون در اثر نیش ریتر مرد...  وقتی دوباره چشماشو باز کرد، متوجه شد که به گذشته برگشته، زمانی قبل از درگیر شدن با شاهزاده دوم ریتر. تو این موقعیت بیشتر چی نیاز داری؟! درسته! سرعت! اون فوراً به قلمرو پدرش رفت.  "خوش اومدی بانو!"  "خدای من! تا این حد بزرگ شدی…”  "بانوی جوان با پاهای کوچیکش زیبا راه میره!"  هه، چطور ممکنه که با چنین استقبال گرمی روبرو بشم؟

column65: fr:"Beatty est une enfant provenant d'une puissante famille de lions métamorphes
column66: cependant elle est née en tant qu'écureuil. Étant séparée de son père et de son frère ainé
column67: elle se retrouve à vivre chez sa tante.\n\nMaltraitée
column68: la pauvre enfant se trouve un ami dans cette tragédie
column71: qui se trouve être un métamorphe serpent. Elle lui avoue son rêve de partir de chez sa tante à ses 18 ans. Grandissant dans l'espoir d'avoir une vie meilleure
column72: une fois atteint de ses 18 ans tout s'effondre: il s'avère que Liter était du côté de sa tante pendant tout ce temps et qu'il ne nourri aucun sentiment d'amitié à son égard.\n\nElle meurt
column73: empoisonnée par le venin du serpent.\n\nGrâce à une étrange magie
column74: elle parvient à revenir dans le temps
column75: à une époque où elle vient de rencontrer le second prince
column76: pas de temps à perdre! Elle le gifle et s'enfuit sur ses pattes d'écureuil afin de retrouver son père et son frère.\n\nDéterminée à rester avec sa nouvelle famille
column77:
elle trouve toutes sortes de moyens de faciliter la vie de son nouveau peuple.

Ancak bazı sebeplerden dolayı başkentte teyzemin evinde tacize uğrayarak hayatımı yaşamak zorunda kaldım.
Tek arkadaşım ve nişanlım ikinci prense hayalimi gerçekleştirmek için gideceğimi söyledim ancak o bana ihanet etti ve…

‘Rither
column129:
seni piç..!’

Gözlerimi yeniden açtığımda çocukluğumda
column130:
Rither ile ilk karşılaştığımız zamandaydım.
Böyle zamanlarda neye ihtiyacınız vardır? Tabii ki hız.
Plan yapmakla falan uğraşmadım ve hemen babam Dük Aslan’ın topraklarına kaçtım.

Hoş karşılanmasam da gelecekte keşfedilecek olan bu büyük bir sırrı bildiğim için…

“Hoş geldiniz leydim!”
“AMman tanrıçam! Ne ara bu kadar büyüdünüz…?”
“Leydim tombiş ayaklarıyla yürüyor!”
Ha? Neden böyle karşılandım?

Olmaz

en:"Aria offered a contract marriage. To Grand Duke Valentine who was said to have sold his soul to the devil. So she could protect herself and him.

"Marry me."

Aria passed him a note which asked for his hand in marriage with her little maple leaf like hands.

"It's a contract marriage so we'll divorce 10 years later..."

The young master grabbed the note Aria was writing and ripped it to shreds.

"So where do I stamp it?"

"You told me you'll divorce me once we're older."

The young devil grew up and kissed her forehead.

"Since we have become adults
column43:
we have to instead make a contract for adults."

column22: description:{"en":"Love comes in many forms. A magnificent bird comforts a struggling girl; a vampire waltzes with a young lady at night; a blind girl lives with a monster of whom there is more than meets the eye. This six-story manga collection by masterful manga creator Nagabe explores fascinating relationships that refuse to be confined.\n\n1. *Daisy
column23: Mata Ashita* (デージー、またあした
column25: Daisy*): A frail girl recovers with the help of an unlikely friend.\n2. *Ookami Ningen to Ningen Ookami* (オオカミニンゲンとにんげんおおかみ
column26: *Man-Wolf and Wolf-Girl*): A man-wolf takes in a wild child.\n3. *Hijoushoku to Gochisou* (非常食とごちそう
column27: *A Feast of Emergency Rations*): A humanoid vulture takes in a little girl.\n4. *Mayonaka no Waltz* (まよなかのワルツ
column28: *Midnight Waltz*): A girl makes the acquaintance of a monstrous creature who believes himself to be quite human.\n5. *Shiro no Ou-sama* (しろ の おうさま
column29: *The White King*): An albino boy and a white lion form a unique bond.\n6. *Mienai Hito-tachi* (みえないひとたち
column30: *Invisible People*): The blind girl lives with a mysterious creature that somehow protects her. But the girl was aware. The creature is \"a horrible monster.\"\n\n**Note:** Stories 1 through 5 are included in  *[Love Stories Between Different Species](https://mangadex.org/title/4cc14713-e34c-456f-a8a1-a07084240199)*."
column31: es:"Nagabe nos ofrece seis historias de amor entre niños y criaturas no humanas. Una recopilación de breves gemas en las que se construyen relaciones profundas y diversas. Historias recopiladas:\n1. *Hasta mañana
column32: Daisy*: Un pájaro gigante visita y ofrece regalos cada día a una niña enferma.\n2. *El hombre lobo y la lobezna humana*: Un lobo da cariño y una vida humana a una niña.\n3. *Ración de emergencia y festín*: Un pájaro antropomorfo recoge a una niña. ¿Será una mera ración de emergencia
column33: un festín u otra cosa?\n4. *El vals de medianoche*: Cada noche se celebra un baile. En él
column34: un vampiro y una niña danzan juntos.\n5. *El rey blanco*: Un humano frágil de tez pálida y una poderosa bestia blanca encerrada en una jaula.\n6. *Aquellos a los que no veo: Una niña ciega convive con un monstruo de aspecto aterrador."

column47:
ja:"少女たちと――…大鳥、狼、鳥人、吸血鬼、ライオン、化け物。 
ながべが描くヘンテコな愛の物語。 

●収録作品● 
1. 「デージー、またあした。」 
贈り物を携えて、大鳥は足の悪い少女のもとを毎日訪れる。 
2. 「オオカミニンゲンとにんげんおおかみ。」 
狼が少女に与えるのは人間らしい暮らしと、愛。 
3. 「非常食とご馳走。」 
鳥人がひろった少女は“非常食"か“ごちそう"か、あるいは…。 
4. 「まよなかのワルツ」 
毎夜開かれる小さな舞踏会。少女と吸血鬼はワルツを踊る。 
5. 「しろ の おうさま。」 
檻の中で生きる白くて強い獣と、白くて弱い人間。 
6. 「みえないひとたち。」 
目の見えない少女は"醜くおそろしい化け物"と暮らす。 

『異種恋愛物語集』収録作品を中心に、人外×少女の読み切り六作品を収録。 
多様で豊かな関係性が描かれる珠玉の短編集がここに。"

column7: description:{"en":"The story is set in a dystopian alternative present where any kind of substance able to alter the state of mind is legalized and authorized for consumption at home or in designated places called Pomp Bars.  \nThese products

column16: he takes the picture and runs away. He later finds out that she is an actress by the name of Shinomiya Sana. A TV drama
column18: will be shot in Shouta's town and Sana will be starring in one of the lead roles
column19: as a passionate girl who whole-heartedly chases after the guy she loves. However
column20: Sana has never experienced that kind of love. To practice for this role (and maybe truly fall in love) Sana asks Shouta to be her boyfriend!"

column25: истинного спутника жизни. Известная школьная актриса работает над фильмом в основе сюжета которого лежит эта легенда. Наш главный герой по уши в неё влюблен
column27: чтобы рассказать о своих чувствах. Однажды
column28: он случайно встречает её в школе и помогает избежать встречи с приставучими фанатами. Поговорив с ней он выясняет
column29: что сразу после средней школы она начала работать как актриса и у неё просто не было времени на личную жизнь
column30: а следовательно у неё совсем нет опыта для игры в таком фильме. Поэтому

column42:
sent a marriage proposal to Cecil. She got dragged to the empire unwillingly but when she saw the emperor's face she had a change of heart.

"You're quite the hottie aren't you?"

 She liked her husband. And her husband likes her back too! To live happily with her tyrant husband does Cecil need to become a villainess far worse than the tyrant?!

---
“I would rather just go out with a bang!”

For Princess Cecile
column43: being married off to the emperor of a neighboring empire was unavoidable. But wait
column44: isn’t this the same Emperor Estian who's notorious for being a heartless sadist?  In order to maintain her final shred of dignity
column45: the fearless Cecile demands that her future husband carry her all the way from the carriage to the wedding chapel! If this is her fate
column46: she might as well put up a fight before dying at the hands of the handsome emperor. After all
column47:
the only way to fight fire is with… more fire?! Can Cecile become a villain even more fearsome than her tyrant husband? Based on the hit novel.

ja:"ある日突然、前世の記憶が蘇った少女ローザ・ベロニカ。
彼女は今いる世界が、前世で読んだ恋愛ファンタジー小説の世界であることを知る。 
そんな彼女の前に使者が現れ、小説のサブキャラ「ロゼンタ・エステラ」の父 カリゴ・エステラ公爵のもとへと連れていかれる。
そして公爵から衝撃的な発言を聞く。 
「お前はこれより、エステラ家の唯一の公子 　ロゼンタ・エステラとして生きろ」
あれ？ロゼンタ・エステラって男じゃなかったの！？ 
私が彼で…彼が私？ 

ドタバタ恋愛ファンタジーが今始まる！ 
事実は小説より奇なり…？
